<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0006', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:198'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='198:213'>　毛詩陸疏廣要　　　　詩類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='213:219'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:248'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案毛詩陸疏廣要四卷吳陸璣撰明毛晋注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='248:273'>　　　　晋原名鳯苞字子晋常熟人家富圖籍世傳影宋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='273:297'>　　　　本多所蔵收又喜傳刻古書汲古閣板至今流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='297:320'>　　　　布天下故在明季以博雅好事名一時嘗刻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='320:343'>　　　　津逮秘書十五集皆宋元以前舊帙惟此書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='343:369'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0006', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='369:392'>　　　　為晉所自編陸璣原本二卷每卷又分二子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='392:415'>　　　　卷葢儲藏本富故徵引易繁採摭既多故異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='415:438'>　　　　同滋甚辯難考訂其説不能不長也其中如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='438:461'>　　　　南山有臺一條則引韻書證其佚脱有集維</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='461:484'>　　　　鷮一條則引詩緝證其異同其考訂亦頗不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='484:507'>　　　　苟至於嗜異貪多每傷支蔓如鶴鳴於九皋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='507:530'>　　　　一條後附焦山瘞鶴銘考一篇蔓延及於石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='530:553'>　　　　刻於經義渺無所闗核以詁經之古法殊乖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='553:579'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0006', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='579:602'>　　　　體例然雖傷冗碎究勝空踈明季説詩之家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='602:625'>　　　　往往簸弄聰明變聖經為小品晉獨言言徵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='625:648'>　　　　實固宜過而存之是亦所謂論其世矣乾隆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='648:663'>　　　　四十六年四月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='663:695'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='695:721'>　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span><br/>
</p>
